<br>
Remember, the grouping formula is -<br>
(your level) x 1.5 = highest level person you can group with and still gain xp &amp; avoid TLC<br>
<br>
If you are level 61 and there is a level 40 in the group, TLC takes effect &amp; no xp is gained. 40 x 1.5 = 60<br>
<br>
Raid removes the level restrictions on groups in exchange for the raid experience penalty<br>
